field.div:
% set base_url = object.env['ir.config_parameter'].get_param('web.base.url') + '/web?#'
% set record_id = object.id or ''
% set view_type = 'form'
% set model = 'purchase.request'
% set action = object.env.ref('atta_purchase_request.purchase_request_action').id or ''
% set menu_id = object.env.ref('atta_purchase_request.purchase_request_menu_root').id or ''
% set params = {
'id': record_id,
'view_type': view_type,
'model': model,
'action': action,
'menu_id': menu_id
}
% set access_url = base_url + urlencode(params)








     1ST LEVEL APPROVAL FOR PURCHASE REQUEST: ${object.name}









Dear ${object.department_id.manager_id.user_id.name or ''},

The purchase request ${object.name} has been submitted by ${object.create_uid.name or ''}.

Below is some information of the purchase request:




Requester: ${','.join(object.create_uid.employee_ids and object.create_uid.employee_ids.mapped('name') or '')}

Department: ${object.department_id and object.department_id.name or ''}

Description: ${object.description or ''}

Requested Delivery Date: ${object.request_deliver_date or '' }



Please click to ${object.name} for detail information!

Best Regards.











${object.company_id.name}
       % if user.company_id.phone:

Phone: ${object.company_id.phone}
       % endif
       % if user.company_id.email:

Email: ${object.company_id.email}
       % endif
       % if user.company_id.website:

Website: ${object.company_id.website}
       % endif






